Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.97,0:16:39.83,Default,,0,0,0,,果然是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.05,0:16:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,摩拉克斯！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.05,0:16:41.00,ENG,,0,0,0,,{\pos(931.5,985)}Marax
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.05,0:16:41.00,NOTE,,0,0,0,,{\an9}注：摩拉克斯 所罗门72柱魔神中排名第21位
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.61,0:16:43.58,Default,,0,0,0,,可恶…！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.59,0:16:46.41,Default,,0,0,0,,这孩子还是一样爱乱来呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.01,0:16:47.86,Default,,0,0,0,,我们继续前进吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.38,0:16:49.38,Default,,0,0,0,,放着他不管可以吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.86,0:16:54.27,Default,,0,0,0,,没事的 那孩子每次乱来的结果基本上都是正确的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.69,0:16:57.44,Default,,0,0,0,,引到这边来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.03,0:17:08.36,Default,,0,0,0,,另一架 从后方跟紧它！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.41,0:17:15.24,Default,,0,0,0,,如果攻击后方无装甲的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.40,0:17:16.47,Default,,0,0,0,,就可以打到它的引擎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.03,0:17:19.41,Default,,0,0,0,,后方又出现了2机
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.57,0:17:22.60,Default,,0,0,0,,方向175 沿着海岸线来飞
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.14,0:17:24.41,Default,,0,0,0,,雪姐 能听到我说话吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.62,0:17:26.88,Default,,0,0,0,,把我呼之即来挥之即去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.27,0:17:28.39,Default,,0,0,0,,方向保持不变！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.95,0:17:38.13,Default,,0,0,0,,布提斯…摩拉克斯…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.95,0:17:38.13,ENG,,0,0,0,,{\pos(795,985)}Botis
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.95,0:17:38.13,ENG,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1045.5,985)}Marax
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.42,0:17:40.39,Default,,0,0,0,,罗诺比 …哈帕斯…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.42,0:17:40.39,ENG,,0,0,0,,{\pos(816,985)}Ronove
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.42,0:17:40.39,ENG,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1051.5,985)}Halphas
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.50,0:17:42.55,Default,,0,0,0,,劳姆…拜恩…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.50,0:17:42.55,ENG,,0,0,0,,{\pos(847.5,985)}Raum
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.50,0:17:42.55,ENG,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1017,985)}Vine
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.82,0:17:46.32,Default,,0,0,0,,竟敢伤害我的孩子们…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.55,0:17:48.81,Default,,0,0,0,,同时攻击哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.31,0:17:49.97,Default,,0,0,0,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.45,0:17:52.41,Default,,0,0,0,,那么 就拿出我的杀手锏！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.69,0:18:08.51,Default,,0,0,0,,飞走了…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.03,0:18:12.00,Default,,0,0,0,,可恶！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.18,0:18:13.14,Default,,0,0,0,,那是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.39,0:18:14.37,Default,,0,0,0,,我也不知道！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.62,0:18:17.72,Default,,0,0,0,,它拉开了距离 开始加速了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.82,0:18:19.46,Default,,0,0,0,,用狙击打偏它的轨道！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.73,0:18:21.69,Default,,0,0,0,,那么大的体型用步枪是没用的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.71,0:18:24.26,Default,,0,0,0,,现在挂着你 机体太沉了躲不开
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.22,0:18:27.82,Default,,0,0,0,,看我把你们撞散
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.40,0:18:31.42,Default,,0,0,0,,它来了 蝙蝠！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.43,0:18:33.16,Default,,0,0,0,,给我闭嘴 橙色的家伙！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.38,0:18:38.46,Default,,0,0,0,,竟然躲开了?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.12,0:18:43.21,Default,,0,0,0,,让机体失速下降了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.04,0:18:48.74,Default,,0,0,0,,又来了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.88,0:18:50.03,Default,,0,0,0,,拉不起来…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.45,0:18:51.93,Default,,0,0,0,,同样的手段对我可行不通
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.26,0:18:56.32,Default,,0,0,0,,结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.26,0:19:04.21,Default,,0,0,0,,发生什么事？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.23,0:19:33.83,Default,,0,0,0,,那是什么…？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.27,0:19:35.12,Default,,0,0,0,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.92,0:19:39.88,Default,,0,0,0,,飞空艇？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.46,0:19:41.10,Default,,0,0,0,,不…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.49,0:19:44.49,Default,,0,0,0,,是战舰吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.60,0:19:49.46,Default,,0,0,0,,找到你了！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.28,0:19:51.28,Default,,0,0,0,,亚瑟拉姆公主！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.61,0:19:52.56,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么可能！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.46,0:19:57.76,Default,,0,0,0,,没有Aldnoah的地球人为什么会驾驶着这样的战舰！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.98,0:20:00.61,Default,,0,0,0,,12点钟方向敌机接近
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.80,0:20:01.72,Default,,0,0,0,,这是碰撞路线！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.38,0:20:13.91,Default,,0,0,0,,可恶的地球人！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.74,0:20:16.45,Default,,0,0,0,,请准备应对冲击！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.54,0:20:26.76,Default,,0,0,0,,可恶 还没结束！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.54,0:20:35.27,Default,,0,0,0,,所有的火星人都是我父亲的仇人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.27,0:20:42.22,Default,,0,0,0,,我们成功了呢！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.93,0:20:49.55,Default,,0,0,0,,终于找到你了 亚瑟拉姆公主
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.02,0:20:52.10,Default,,0,0,0,,公主已经死了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.66,0:20:57.14,Default,,0,0,0,,可是 你为什么还在找她？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.80,0:21:02.16,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道公主还活着
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.16,0:21:04.03,Default,,0,0,0,,这是为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.34,0:21:06.57,Default,,0,0,0,,你这话是什么意思？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.45,0:21:08.29,Default,,0,0,0,,回答我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.87,0:21:11.49,Default,,0,0,0,,请让我和公主见一面
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.26,0:21:13.72,Default,,0,0,0,,先回答我的问题
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.99,0:21:20.47,Default,,0,0,0,,难道…你想利用公主吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.68,0:21:25.15,Default,,0,0,0,,如果我要利用她 你有意见吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.29,0:21:29.45,Default,,0,0,0,,你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.73,0:21:49.12,Default,,0,0,0,,你是我的敌人吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.81,0:21:55.66,Default,,0,0,0,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.36,0:21:59.61,Default,,0,0,0,,是我的敌人
